Reasoning: The paper deals with visual servoing, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method uses a neural network for camera pose estimation, which involves computer vision techniques (cs.CV). The use of a Siamese architecture for the neural network suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the robustness of the network, which could involve machine learning techniques for handling variations in data (cs.AI). Finally, the application of the method to an industrial robot suggests a focus on control systems (cs.SY).
